142
00:09:59,870 --> 00:10:02,650
I wonder how Lin is doing.

143
00:10:06,310 --> 00:10:08,520
I think Lin’s going to be fine.

144
00:10:09,360 --> 00:10:11,150
Lin is great.

145
00:10:11,700 --> 00:10:14,980
She was able to make Tong concentrate on his studies, remember?

146
00:10:16,440 --> 00:10:17,240
Trust me.

147
00:10:17,260 --> 00:10:18,510
Lin will be fine.

148
00:10:20,840 --> 00:10:22,070
I think so too.

149
00:10:23,480 --> 00:10:24,890
Don’t think too much.

150
00:10:24,920 --> 00:10:26,240
