152
00:10:31,560 --> 00:10:33,140
She was your first love.

153
00:10:38,690 --> 00:10:39,570
You know what?

154
00:10:41,150 --> 00:10:44,760
I had a crush on Lin from the first day of school.

155
00:10:50,400 --> 00:10:52,710
Lin was the first love for all of you, wasn’t she?

156
00:10:53,390 --> 00:10:54,170
Yeah.

157
00:10:54,480 --> 00:10:55,640
The whole gang liked her.

158
00:10:58,080 --> 00:10:59,240
Did you know

159
00:11:00,520 --> 00:11:02,070
