160
00:11:05,440 --> 00:11:06,200
Of course.

161
00:11:06,440 --> 00:11:07,370
It was Tong.

162
00:11:08,290 --> 00:11:09,750
I knew that long ago.

163
00:11:11,400 --> 00:11:14,450
Tong must be dead worried about Lin.

164
00:12:03,680 --> 00:12:05,080
I hope you’re safe, Lin.

165
00:12:07,620 --> 00:12:08,620
Hello, Tong.

166
00:12:10,090 --> 00:12:10,960
Hello, Lin.

167
00:12:11,590 --> 00:12:13,020
How are you doing?

168
00:12:13,040 --> 00:12:15,020
