173
00:12:21,680 --> 00:12:22,460
I’m fine.

174
00:12:22,480 --> 00:12:23,960
I’m safe.

175
00:12:24,390 --> 00:12:27,540
I was in town during the time the Tsunami hit.

176
00:12:28,500 --> 00:12:29,700
Don’t worry, Tong.

177
00:12:29,990 --> 00:12:31,160
I’m fine.

178
00:12:35,900 --> 00:12:38,420
Where are you right now?

179
00:12:41,360 --> 00:12:43,600
I’m at the temporary shelter.

180
00:12:43,730 --> 00:12:45,310
It seems chaotic here.

181
00:12:46,170 --> 00:12:47,650
Full of people who are injured

182
00:12:47,970 --> 00:12:50,640
and people looking for their families.

183
00:12:58,800 --> 00:13:00,070
You’re okay, right?

184
00:13:01,030 --> 00:13:02,050
I’m fine.

185
00:13:02,880 --> 00:13:04,800
I’ve just talked to Ma and Pa.

186
00:13:06,110 --> 00:13:07,370
You know what, Lin?

187
00:13:08,250 --> 00:13:09,620
I was so scared

188
00:13:10,940 --> 00:13:12,440
