195
00:13:39,070 --> 00:13:40,250
Thanks, Tong.

196
00:13:45,370 --> 00:13:46,040
Then

197
00:13:48,040 --> 00:13:49,190
that’s that.

198
00:13:50,000 --> 00:13:51,000
Hold on.

199
00:13:59,820 --> 00:14:01,080
You miss me, don’t you?

200
00:14:02,920 --> 00:14:04,920
That’s what they mean when they say

201
00:14:05,640 --> 00:14:09,900
when in crisis, you’ll think of the face of the one you love.

202
00:14:12,200 --> 00:14:14,310
I can’t remember your face anymore.

203
00:14:15,800 --> 00:14:17,560
We haven’t met in two years.

204
00:14:18,880 --> 00:14:19,740
Come on.

205
00:14:22,150 --> 00:14:23,780
How can you forget my handsome face?

206
00:14:25,500 --> 00:14:28,570
How have you been over the past two years?

207
00:14:29,500 --> 00:14:30,840
Did you study hard?

208
00:14:34,910 --> 00:14:37,010
We haven’t talked in two years

209
00:14:38,560 --> 00:14:39,990
and you’re asking me about my studies?

210
00:14:41,720 --> 00:14:44,360
Because you tend to not pay attention to your study.

211
00:14:45,750 --> 00:14:46,880
I’m just worried.

212
00:14:56,550 --> 00:14:58,550
I’ve become way more keen on my studies.

213
00:15:02,640 --> 00:15:04,320
It’s actually because of you

214
00:15:05,370 --> 00:15:07,360
for making me more keen on my studies.

215
00:15:08,000 --> 00:15:09,360
You’re a sweet talker.

216
00:15:15,420 --> 00:15:16,270
So…

217
00:15:19,400 --> 00:15:21,400
Are you seeing anyone right now?

218
00:15:24,510 --> 00:15:25,840
I’m not telling you.

219
00:15:28,280 --> 00:15:30,280
But I was with Pao for a while.

220
00:15:31,450 --> 00:15:32,400
I knew that.

221
00:15:34,300 --> 00:15:35,190
Then

222
00:15:37,240 --> 00:15:38,420
