223
00:15:39,750 --> 00:15:43,610
I felt like Pao didn’t really like me.

224
00:15:45,200 --> 00:15:46,430
That’s not true.

225
00:15:47,130 --> 00:15:49,980
Pao is crazy about you.

226
00:15:50,430 --> 00:15:52,310
He probably likes you from head to toe.

227
00:15:53,080 --> 00:15:55,670
Ever since I got the love from you,

228
00:15:58,260 --> 00:16:02,370
