250
00:18:37,320 --> 00:18:38,150
Lin.

251
00:18:41,840 --> 00:18:44,050
Do you believe in a parallel universe?

252
00:18:54,260 --> 00:18:55,310
Perhaps,

253
00:18:57,930 --> 00:18:59,250
