255
00:19:13,980 --> 00:19:15,880
I’m envious of them.

256
00:19:28,720 --> 00:19:30,530
Thanks for liking me, Tong.

257
00:19:35,950 --> 00:19:37,410
I have to go.

258
00:19:39,480 --> 00:19:40,670
I’ll hang up now.

259
00:20:19,330 --> 00:20:20,940
(Getting to talk to Lin again made me realize)

260
00:20:22,150 --> 00:20:25,770
(that the worst mistake I made)

261
00:20:28,000 --> 00:20:30,860
(was to not have contacted Lin over the two years.)

